{
  "video_id": "bZsn1_DARRs",
  "title": "Fashion has a pollution problem -- can biology fix it? | Natsai Audrey Chieza",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12840.0,
      "end_time": 15879.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re watching the life cycle of a Streptomyces coelicolor."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17520.0,
      "end_time": 19896.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a strain of bacteria that&#39;s found in the soil"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19920.0,
      "end_time": 22336.0,
      "text": "where it lives in a community with other organisms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22360.0,
      "end_time": 23680.0,
      "text": "decomposing organic matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24680.0,
      "end_time": 26600.0,
      "text": "Coelicolor is a beautiful organism."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27160.0,
      "end_time": 30320.0,
      "text": "A powerhouse for synthesizing organic chemical compounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31160.0,
      "end_time": 34136.0,
      "text": "It produces an antibiotic called actinorhodin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34160.0,
      "end_time": 38736.0,
      "text": "which ranges in color from blue to pink and purple,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38760.0,
      "end_time": 41000.0,
      "text": "depending on the acidity of its environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 41920.0,
      "end_time": 45560.0,
      "text": "That it produces these pigment molecules sparked my curiosity"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45800.0,
      "end_time": 47480.0,
      "text": "and led me to collaborate closely with coelicolor."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48280.0,
      "end_time": 50336.0,
      "text": "It is an unlikely partnership,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50360.0,
      "end_time": 54720.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s one that completely transformed my practice as a materials designer."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55560.0,
      "end_time": 59976.0,
      "text": "From it, I understood how nature was going to completely revolutionize"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 60000.0,
      "end_time": 62856.0,
      "text": "how we design and build our environments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62880.0,
      "end_time": 65336.0,
      "text": "and that organisms like coelicolor"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65360.0,
      "end_time": 67679.0,
      "text": "were going to help us grow our material future."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 68720.0,
      "end_time": 71520.0,
      "text": "So what&#39;s wrong with things as they are?"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 72560.0,
      "end_time": 73896.0,
      "text": "Well, for the last century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 73920.0,
      "end_time": 76976.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve organized ourselves around fossil fuels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 77000.0,
      "end_time": 80560.0,
      "text": "arguably, the most valuable material system we have ever known."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 80800.0,
      "end_time": 83776.0,
      "text": "We are tethered to this resource, and we&#39;ve crafted a dependency on it"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 83800.0,
      "end_time": 88840.0,
      "text": "that defines our identities, cultures, our ways of making and our economies."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 89360.0,
      "end_time": 93856.0,
      "text": "But our fossil fuel-based activities are reshaping the earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 93880.0,
      "end_time": 98455.0,
      "text": "with a kind of violence that is capable of dramatically changing the climate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 98480.0,
      "end_time": 101856.0,
      "text": "of accelerating a loss of biodiversity"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 101880.0,
      "end_time": 103839.0,
      "text": "and even sustaining human conflict."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 104640.0,
      "end_time": 105896.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re living in a world"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 105920.0,
      "end_time": 109480.0,
      "text": "where the denial of this dependence has become deadly."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 110200.0,
      "end_time": 112136.0,
      "text": "And its reasons are multiple,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 112160.0,
      "end_time": 116576.0,
      "text": "but they include the privilege of not being affected"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 116600.0,
      "end_time": 120336.0,
      "text": "and what I believe is a profound lack of imagination"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 120360.0,
      "end_time": 122376.0,
      "text": "about how else we could live"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 122400.0,
      "end_time": 125400.0,
      "text": "within the limits of this planet&#39;s boundaries."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 126200.0,
      "end_time": 130816.0,
      "text": "Fossil fuels will one day give way to renewable energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 130840.0,
      "end_time": 133216.0,
      "text": "That means we need to find new material systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 133240.0,
      "end_time": 135336.0,
      "text": "that are not petroleum-based."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 135360.0,
      "end_time": 138800.0,
      "text": "I believe that those material systems will be biological,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 139800.0,
      "end_time": 142175.0,
      "text": "but what matters is how we design and build them."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 142199.0,
      "end_time": 146240.0,
      "text": "They mustn&#39;t perpetuate the destructive legacies of the oil age."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 147960.0,
      "end_time": 150560.0,
      "text": "When you look at this image,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 150800.0,
      "end_time": 151280.0,
      "text": "what do you see?"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 153680.0,
      "end_time": 157296.0,
      "text": "Well, I see a highly sophisticated biological system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 157320.0,
      "end_time": 159376.0,
      "text": "that through the use of enzymes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 159400.0,
      "end_time": 162456.0,
      "text": "can move and place atoms more quickly and precisely"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 162480.0,
      "end_time": 164399.0,
      "text": "than anything we&#39;ve ever engineered."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 165120.0,
      "end_time": 167880.0,
      "text": "And we know that it can do this at scale."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 168920.0,
      "end_time": 171815.0,
      "text": "Nature has evolved over 3.8 billion years"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 171840.0,
      "end_time": 173696.0,
      "text": "to be able to do this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 173720.0,
      "end_time": 176696.0,
      "text": "but now through the use of synthetic biology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 176720.0,
      "end_time": 178336.0,
      "text": "an emerging scientific discipline"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 178360.0,
      "end_time": 182336.0,
      "text": "that seeks to customize this functionality of living systems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 182360.0,
      "end_time": 186800.0,
      "text": "we can now rapid prototype the assembly of DNA."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 187120.0,
      "end_time": 191536.0,
      "text": "That means that we can engineer the kind of biological precision"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 191560.0,
      "end_time": 196960.0,
      "text": "that makes it possible to design a bacteria"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 196120.0,
      "end_time": 198216.0,
      "text": "that can recycle metal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 198240.0,
      "end_time": 200216.0,
      "text": "to grow fungi into furniture"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 200240.0,
      "end_time": 204400.0,
      "text": "and even sequester renewable energy from algae."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 204840.0,
      "end_time": 209656.0,
      "text": "To think about how we might access this inherent brilliance of nature --"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 209680.0,
      "end_time": 212456.0,
      "text": "to build things from living things --"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 212480.0,
      "end_time": 215616.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s consider the biological process of fermentation."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 215640.0,
      "end_time": 219296.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve come to think of fermentation, when harnessed by humans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 219320.0,
      "end_time": 222576.0,
      "text": "as an advanced technological toolkit for our survival."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 222600.0,
      "end_time": 224656.0,
      "text": "When a solid or a liquid ferments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 224680.0,
      "end_time": 227240.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s chemically broken down by bacterial fungi."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 227880.0,
      "end_time": 229976.0,
      "text": "The byproduct of this is what we value."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 230000.0,
      "end_time": 233480.0,
      "text": "So for example, we add yeast to grapes to make wine."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 234840.0,
      "end_time": 239336.0,
      "text": "Well in nature, these transformations are part of a complex network --"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 239360.0,
      "end_time": 242376.0,
      "text": "a continuous cycle that redistributes energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 242400.0,
      "end_time": 245256.0,
      "text": "Fermentation gives rise to multispecies interactions"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 245280.0,
      "end_time": 247416.0,
      "text": "of bacteria and fungi,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 247440.0,
      "end_time": 250560.0,
      "text": "plants, insects, animals and humans:"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 250800.0,
      "end_time": 252240.0,
      "text": "in other words, whole ecosystems."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 253120.0,
      "end_time": 256776.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve known about these powerful microbial interactions"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 256800.0,
      "end_time": 258976.0,
      "text": "for thousands of years."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 259000.0,
      "end_time": 261896.0,
      "text": "You can see how through the fermentation of grains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 261920.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264576.0,
      "text": "vegetal matter and animal products,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 264600.0,
      "end_time": 269296.0,
      "text": "all peoples and cultures of the world have domesticated microorganisms"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 269320.0,
      "end_time": 270920.0,
      "text": "to make the inedible edible."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 271839.0,
      "end_time": 276176.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s even evidence that as early as 350 AD,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 276200.0,
      "end_time": 280440.0,
      "text": "people deliberately fermented foodstuffs that contained antibiotics."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 281400.0,
      "end_time": 283696.0,
      "text": "The skeletal remains of some Sudanese Nubian"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 283720.0,
      "end_time": 287576.0,
      "text": "were found to contain significant deposits of tetracycline."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 287600.0,
      "end_time": 290440.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s an antibiotic that we use in modern medicine today."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 291440.0,
      "end_time": 294936.0,
      "text": "And nearly 1500 years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 294960.0,
      "end_time": 299416.0,
      "text": "Alexander Fleming discovered the antimicrobial properties of mold."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 299440.0,
      "end_time": 303976.0,
      "text": "And it was only through the industrialized fermentation of penicillin"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 304000.0,
      "end_time": 306720.0,
      "text": "that millions could survive infectious diseases."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 307520.0,
      "end_time": 310695.0,
      "text": "Fermentation could once again play an important role"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 310720.0,
      "end_time": 313160.0,
      "text": "in our human development."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 313400.0,
      "end_time": 315696.0,
      "text": "Could it represent a new mode of survival"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 315720.0,
      "end_time": 319400.0,
      "text": "if we harness it to completely change our industries?"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 319880.0,
      "end_time": 323376.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve worked in my creative career to develop new material systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 323400.0,
      "end_time": 324936.0,
      "text": "for the textile industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 324960.0,
      "end_time": 327215.0,
      "text": "And while it is work that I love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 327240.0,
      "end_time": 329955.0,
      "text": "I cannot reconcile with the fact that the textile industry"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 329979.0,
      "end_time": 332256.0,
      "text": "is one of the most polluting in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 332280.0,
      "end_time": 337950.0,
      "text": "Most of the ecological harm caused by textile processing"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 337120.0,
      "end_time": 339400.0,
      "text": "occurs at the finishing and the dyeing stage."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 340840.0,
      "end_time": 344440.0,
      "text": "Processing textiles requires huge amounts of water."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 345120.0,
      "end_time": 349536.0,
      "text": "And since the oil age completely transformed the textile industry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 349560.0,
      "end_time": 350816.0,
      "text": "many of the materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 350840.0,
      "end_time": 355376.0,
      "text": "and the chemicals used to process them are petroleum based."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 355400.0,
      "end_time": 359799.0,
      "text": "And so coupled with our insatiable appetite for fast fashion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 360680.0,
      "end_time": 365376.0,
      "text": "a huge amount of textile waste is ending up in landfill every year"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 365400.0,
      "end_time": 368760.0,
      "text": "because it remains notoriously difficult to recycle."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 369640.0,
      "end_time": 373960.0,
      "text": "So again, contrast this with biology."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 373120.0,
      "end_time": 376216.0,
      "text": "Evolved over 3.8 billion years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 376240.0,
      "end_time": 378960.0,
      "text": "to rapid prototype,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 378120.0,
      "end_time": 380696.0,
      "text": "to recycle and to replenish"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 380720.0,
      "end_time": 383400.0,
      "text": "better than any system we&#39;ve ever engineered."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 384480.0,
      "end_time": 386816.0,
      "text": "I was inspired by this immense potential"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 386840.0,
      "end_time": 390775.0,
      "text": "and wanted to explore it through a seemingly simple question --"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 390800.0,
      "end_time": 392000.0,
      "text": "at the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 392880.0,
      "end_time": 395376.0,
      "text": "If a bacteria produces a pigment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 395400.0,
      "end_time": 397919.0,
      "text": "how do we work with it to dye textiles?"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 399800.0,
      "end_time": 401455.0,
      "text": "Well, one of my favorite ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 401480.0,
      "end_time": 406536.0,
      "text": "is to grow Streptomyces coelicolor directly onto silk."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 406560.0,
      "end_time": 410800.0,
      "text": "You can see how each colony produces pigment around its own territory."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 411720.0,
      "end_time": 414456.0,
      "text": "Now, if you add many, many cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 414480.0,
      "end_time": 420800.0,
      "text": "they generate enough dyestuff to saturate the entire cloth."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 427120.0,
      "end_time": 430816.0,
      "text": "Now, the magical thing about dyeing textiles in this way --"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 430840.0,
      "end_time": 432416.0,
      "text": "this sort of direct fermentation"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 432440.0,
      "end_time": 436336.0,
      "text": "when you add the bacteria directly onto the silk --"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 436360.0,
      "end_time": 439576.0,
      "text": "is that to dye one t-shirt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 439600.0,
      "end_time": 443440.0,
      "text": "the bacteria survive on just 200 milliliters of water."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 444360.0,
      "end_time": 449656.0,
      "text": "And you can see how this process generates very little runoff"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 449680.0,
      "end_time": 455256.0,
      "text": "and produces a colorfast pigment without the use of any chemicals."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 455280.0,
      "end_time": 456816.0,
      "text": "So now you&#39;re thinking --"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 456840.0,
      "end_time": 459335.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;re thinking right --"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 459360.0,
      "end_time": 464396.0,
      "text": "an inherent problem associated with designing with a living system is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 464420.0,
      "end_time": 467880.0,
      "text": "How do you guide a medium that has a life force of its own?"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 468480.0,
      "end_time": 473856.0,
      "text": "Well, once you&#39;ve established the baseline for cultivating Streptomyces"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 473880.0,
      "end_time": 477960.0,
      "text": "so that it consistently produces enough pigment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 477120.0,
      "end_time": 480176.0,
      "text": "you can turn to twisting, folding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 480200.0,
      "end_time": 483560.0,
      "text": "clamping, dipping, spraying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 483800.0,
      "end_time": 484616.0,
      "text": "submerging --"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 484640.0,
      "end_time": 489640.0,
      "text": "all of these begin to inform the aesthetics of coelicolor&#39;s activity."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 490880.0,
      "end_time": 492616.0,
      "text": "And using them in a systematic way"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 492640.0,
      "end_time": 496360.0,
      "text": "enables us to be able to generate an organic pattern ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 498320.0,
      "end_time": 499520.0,
      "text": "a uniform dye ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 501400.0,
      "end_time": 503800.0,
      "text": "and even a graphic print."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 505240.0,
      "end_time": 511336.0,
      "text": "Another problem is how to scale these artisanal methods of making"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 511360.0,
      "end_time": 515390.0,
      "text": "so that we can start to use them in industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 516799.0,
      "end_time": 518256.0,
      "text": "When we talk about scale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 518280.0,
      "end_time": 520815.0,
      "text": "we consider two things in parallel:"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 520840.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522456.00000000006,
      "text": "scaling the biology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 522480.0,
      "end_time": 525336.0,
      "text": "and then scaling the tools and the processes"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 525360.0,
      "end_time": 527280.0,
      "text": "required to work with the biology."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 528440.0,
      "end_time": 529655.0,
      "text": "If we can do this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 529679.0,
      "end_time": 532550.0,
      "text": "then we can move what happens on a petri dish"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 532800.0,
      "end_time": 534576.0,
      "text": "so that it can meet the human scale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 534600.0,
      "end_time": 538800.0,
      "text": "and then hopefully the architecture of our environments."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 542760.0,
      "end_time": 544176.0,
      "text": "If Fleming were alive today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 544200.0,
      "end_time": 547000.0,
      "text": "this would definitely be a part of his toolkit."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 547760.0,
      "end_time": 550576.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re looking at our current best guess"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 550600.0,
      "end_time": 552400.0,
      "text": "of how to scale biology."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 553280.0,
      "end_time": 554536.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a bioreactor;"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 554560.0,
      "end_time": 557656.0,
      "text": "a kind of microorganism brewery that contains yeasts"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 557680.0,
      "end_time": 562815.0,
      "text": "that have been engineered to produce specific commodity chemicals and compounds"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 562840.0,
      "end_time": 564880.0,
      "text": "like fragrances and flavors."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 565760.0,
      "end_time": 569256.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s actually connected to a suite of automated hardware and software"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 569280.0,
      "end_time": 571216.0,
      "text": "that read in real time"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 571240.0,
      "end_time": 577416.0,
      "text": "and feed back to a design team the growth conditions of the microbe."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 577440.0,
      "end_time": 580536.0,
      "text": "So we can use this system to model the growth characteristics"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 580560.0,
      "end_time": 583175.0,
      "text": "of an organism like coelicolor"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 583200.0,
      "end_time": 586600.0,
      "text": "to see how it would ferment at 50,000 liters."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 587800.0,
      "end_time": 590616.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m currently based at Ginkgo Bioworks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 590640.0,
      "end_time": 593120.0,
      "text": "which is a biotechnology startup in Boston."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 594160.0,
      "end_time": 598496.0,
      "text": "I am working to see how their platform for scaling biology"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 598520.0,
      "end_time": 603776.0,
      "text": "interfaces with my artisanal methods of designing with bacteria for textiles."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 603800.0,
      "end_time": 608960.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re doing things like engineering Streptomyces coelicolor"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 608120.0,
      "end_time": 610600.0,
      "text": "to see if it can produce more pigment."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 611640.0,
      "end_time": 615776.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;re even looking at the tools for synthetic biology."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 615800.0,
      "end_time": 620695.0,
      "text": "Tools that have been designed specifically to automate synthetic biology"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 620720.0,
      "end_time": 624600.0,
      "text": "to see how they could adapt to become tools to print and dye textiles."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 625440.0,
      "end_time": 628496.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m also leveraging digital fabrication,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 628520.0,
      "end_time": 632960.0,
      "text": "because the tools that I need to work with Streptomyces coelicolor"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 632120.0,
      "end_time": 634160.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t actually exist."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 634400.0,
      "end_time": 635575.0,
      "text": "So in this case --"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 635600.0,
      "end_time": 637160.0,
      "text": "in the last week actually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 637400.0,
      "end_time": 639295.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve just designed a petri dish"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 639320.0,
      "end_time": 644136.0,
      "text": "that is engineered to produce a bespoke print on a whole garment."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 644160.0,
      "end_time": 645880.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re making lots of kimonos."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 646760.0,
      "end_time": 648736.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s the exciting thing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 648760.0,
      "end_time": 650136.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 650160.0,
      "end_time": 653550.0,
      "text": "There are others who are building capacity in this field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 653800.0,
      "end_time": 655160.0,
      "text": "like MycoWorks."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 655400.0,
      "end_time": 656776.0,
      "text": "MycoWorks is a startup"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 656800.0,
      "end_time": 659736.0,
      "text": "that wants to replace animal leather with mushroom leather,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 659760.0,
      "end_time": 662415.0,
      "text": "a versatile, high-performance material"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 662440.0,
      "end_time": 666560.0,
      "text": "that has applications beyond textiles and into product and architecture."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 667840.0,
      "end_time": 669576.0,
      "text": "And Bolt Threads --"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 669600.0,
      "end_time": 674856.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve engineered a yeast to produce spider-silk protein"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 674880.0,
      "end_time": 678776.0,
      "text": "that can be spun into a highly programmable yarn."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 678800.0,
      "end_time": 680656.0,
      "text": "So think water resistance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 680680.0,
      "end_time": 683400.0,
      "text": "stretchability and superstrength."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 684480.0,
      "end_time": 686376.0,
      "text": "To reach economies of scale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 686400.0,
      "end_time": 691960.0,
      "text": "these kinds of startups are having to build and design"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 691120.0,
      "end_time": 693920.0,
      "text": "and engineer the infrastructure to work with biology."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 694640.0,
      "end_time": 695856.0,
      "text": "For example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 695880.0,
      "end_time": 699720.0,
      "text": "Bolt Threads have had to engage in some extreme biomimicry."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 700360.0,
      "end_time": 705656.0,
      "text": "To be able to spin the product this yeast creates into a yarn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 705680.0,
      "end_time": 709960.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve engineered a yarn-making machine"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 709120.0,
      "end_time": 712160.0,
      "text": "that mimics the physiological conditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 712400.0,
      "end_time": 715599.0,
      "text": "under which spiders ordinarily spin their own silk."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 716960.0,
      "end_time": 720456.0,
      "text": "So you can start to see how imaginative"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 720480.0,
      "end_time": 726136.0,
      "text": "and inspiring modes of making exist in nature"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 726160.0,
      "end_time": 731815.0,
      "text": "that we can use to build capacity around new bio-based industries."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 731840.0,
      "end_time": 733976.0,
      "text": "What we now have is the technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 734000.0,
      "end_time": 739816.0,
      "text": "to design, build, test and scale these capabilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 739840.0,
      "end_time": 741960.0,
      "text": "At this present moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 741120.0,
      "end_time": 745776.0,
      "text": "as we face the ecological crisis in front of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 745800.0,
      "end_time": 748136.0,
      "text": "what we have to do is to determine"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 748160.0,
      "end_time": 751336.0,
      "text": "how we&#39;re going to build these new material systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 751360.0,
      "end_time": 757136.0,
      "text": "so that they don&#39;t mirror the damaging legacies of the oil age."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 757160.0,
      "end_time": 761616.0,
      "text": "How we&#39;re going to distribute them to ensure a sustainable development"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 761640.0,
      "end_time": 764415.0,
      "text": "that is fair and equitable across the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 764440.0,
      "end_time": 767896.0,
      "text": "And crucially, how we would like the regulatory and ethical frameworks"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 767920.0,
      "end_time": 769376.0,
      "text": "that govern these technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 769400.0,
      "end_time": 770800.0,
      "text": "to interact with our society."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 772400.0,
      "end_time": 776550.0,
      "text": "Biotechnology is going to touch every part of our lived experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 776800.0,
      "end_time": 777296.0,
      "text": "It is living;"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 777320.0,
      "end_time": 778776.0,
      "text": "it is digital;"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 778800.0,
      "end_time": 781575.0,
      "text": "it is designed, and it can be crafted."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 781600.0,
      "end_time": 784720.0,
      "text": "This is a material future that we must be bold enough to shape."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 785360.0,
      "end_time": 786776.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 786800.0,
      "end_time": 789319.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}